OL,3,CGuernsey official heavily criticises
OL,4,CAurigny's summer service
OL,6,FA Guernsey government official will
OL,7,Fmeet with Aurigny bosses to discuss
OL,8,Frecent disruption, including what he
OL,9,Fcalls an "enormously embarrassing"
OL,10,Fplane diversion back to Exeter.
OL,12,FThe President of the States of
OL,13,FGuernsey's Trading and Supervisory
OL,14,FBoard (STSB), Deputy Peter Roffey, is
OL,15,Fmeeting representatives from the
OL,16,FStates-owned airline and Guernsey
OL,17,FPorts to talk through the situation.
