OL,3,CGuernsey official heavily criticises
OL,4,CAurigny's summer service
OL,6,FLast week's disruptions culminated in
OL,7,Fan Aurigny flight being diverted for
OL,8,Farriving too late to Guernsey Airport,
OL,9,Fdespite being on its final descent
OL,10,Fjust 800 feet above the island.
OL,12,FDeputy Roffey says the incident has
OL,13,F"damaged the reputation of Aurigny"
OL,14,Fand that "corners were cut" by both
OL,15,Fthe airline and Guernsey Ports.
OL,17,FHe explains: "The STSB are responsible
OL,18,Fin different ways, we don't run
OL,19,FAurigny but we do run the Ports and
OL,20,Fthat includes the Airport.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
