OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F385A1724246575
OL,3,CGuernsey official heavily criticises
OL,4,CAurigny's summer service
OL,6,F"I find it enormously embarrassing
OL,7,Fthat two organisations in some ways
OL,8,Funder the control of the STSB couldn't
OL,9,Fwork together to make sure that this
OL,10,Fcouldn't possibly happen.
OL,12,F"I'm going to focus on making sure
OL,13,Fthat this can't possibly happen again,
OL,14,Fthat there is a proper working
OL,15,Frelationship between the two bodies,
OL,16,Fand the customer does not have to
OL,17,Fsuffer what those customers did.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
