OL,3,CGuernsey official heavily criticises
OL,4,CAurigny's summer service
OL,6,FAn Aurigny spokesperson says the
OL,7,Fcompany will work with Guernsey Ports
OL,8,Fto seek better resolutions when
OL,9,Fflights are disrupted.
OL,11,FThey add: "We understand the
OL,12,Fimportance of maintaining the
OL,13,Fexcellent reputation of Guernsey and
OL,14,FAlderney for the travelling public and
OL,15,Four tourism industry.
OL,17,F"It has been a challenging period for
OL,18,FAurigny but we continue to have
OL,19,Fconfidence in our airline and look
OL,20,Fforward to having a fully operational
OL,21,Ffleet in the next few months."
